import Noidung from '../edit_tintuc/noidung';
import Noidung6 from '../edit_tintuc/noidung6';
import Noidung7 from '../edit_tintuc/noidung7';
import Noidung8 from '../edit_tintuc/noidung8';
import Tieude from '../edit_tintuc/tieude';

function Xahoi() {
    return (<
        div className="news_xahoi" >
        <
        div className="news_td" >
            <
        div className="td_title" >
                <
                    img src="img/Path_213.png"
                    alt="true"
                    width="7"
                    height="40" />
                <
                    Tieude title="Xã hội" />
                <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        div className="news_nd" >
                    <
                        Noidung6 />
                    <
                        Noidung7 />
                    <
                        Noidung8 />
                    <
        /div> <
        /div>
    );
}
export default Xahoi;
